<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It'd be nice if the insert-method of the Zend_Db_Adapter would support as a third argument  an array of column-value-pairs that sets the ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE parameter.</p>

<p>This will allow us to use REPLACE-functionality that is AFAIK proprietary to MySQL with standard SQL syntax.</p>

